{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/rosetta-code/rosetta-code-challenges/longest-common-subsequence","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"rosetta-code-challenges","demoType":null,"title":"Kraći niz koji je sličan","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p><strong>Najduža zajednička podsekvenca</strong> (ili <strong>LCS</strong>) skupova A i B je najduži skup elemenata iz A i B koji su zajednički između ta dva skupa i koji su u istoj sekvenci u svakom skupu. Na primer, sekvenca <code>1234</code> i <code>1224533324</code> ima LCS od <code>1234</code>:</p>\n<p><u>1234</u></p>\n<p><u>12</u>245<u>3</u>332<u>4</u></p>\n<p>Na primer sekvence slova, razmotrite niz <code>thisisatest</code> i <code>testing123testing</code>. LCS će biti <code>tsitest</code>:</p>\n<p><u>t</u>hi<u>si</u>sa<u>test</u></p>\n<p><u>t</u>e<u>s</u>t<u>i</u>ng123<u>test</u>ing.</p>\n<p>Tvoj kod mora da obrađuje samo niz karaktera.</p>\n</section>","id":"5e6dd1278e6ca105cde40ea9","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Napišite funkciju koja detektuje razliku između velikih i malih slova i vraća LCS za sekvencu od dva slova. Nije potrebno prikazivati više LCS-ova.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Rosetta","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"rosetta-code","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":385271,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/rosetta-code/rosetta-code-challenges/longest-common-subsequence"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function lcs(a, b) {\n\n}","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>lcs</code> Trebalo bi da bude funkcija.</p>","testString":"assert(typeof lcs == 'function');"},{"text":"<p><code>lcs(\"thisisatest\", \"testing123testing\")</code> Trebalo bi da ponovo kreira sekvencu slova.</p>","testString":"assert(typeof lcs('thisisatest', 'testing123testing') == 'string');"},{"text":"<p><code>lcs(\"thisisatest\", \"testing123testing\")</code> treba da obnovi <code>\"tsitest\"</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.equal(lcs('thisisatest', 'testing123testing'), 'tsitest');"},{"text":"<p><code>lcs(\"ABCDGH\", \"AEDFHR\")</code> treba da vrati <code>\"ADH\"</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.equal(lcs('ABCDGH', 'AEDFHR'), 'ADH');"},{"text":"<p><code>lcs(\"AGGTAB\", \"GXTXAYB\")</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>\"GTAB\"</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.equal(lcs('AGGTAB', 'GXTXAYB'), 'GTAB');"},{"text":"<p><code>lcs(\"BDACDB\", \"BDCB\")</code> treba da ponovo učita <code>\"BDCB\"</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.equal(lcs('BDACDB', 'BDCB'), 'BDCB');"},{"text":"<p><code>lcs(\"ABAZDC\", \"BACBAD\")</code> trebalo bi da restaurira <code>\"ABAD\"</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.equal(lcs('ABAZDC', 'BACBAD'), 'ABAD');"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/rosetta-code/#rosetta-code-challenges","dashedName":"longest-common-subsequence","certification":"rosetta-code","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"rosetta-code","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"rosetta-code-challenges","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/rosetta-code/rosetta-code-challenges/longest-increasing-subsequence","prevChallengePath":"/learn/rosetta-code/rosetta-code-challenges/long-multiplication","id":"5e6dd1278e6ca105cde40ea9","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"function ZigZagMatrix(n) {\n  const mtx = [];\n  for (let i = 0; i < n; i++) {\n    mtx[i] = [];\n  }\n\n  let i = 1;\n  let j = 1;\n  for (let e = 0; e < n * n; e++) {\n    mtx[i - 1][j - 1] = e;\n    if ((i + j) % 2 === 0) {\n      // Even stripes\n      if (j < n) j++;\n      else i += 2;\n      if (i > 1) i--;\n    } else {\n      // Odd stripes\n      if (i < n) i++;\n      else j += 2;\n      if (j > 1) j--;\n    }\n  }\n  return mtx;\n}","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/rosetta-code/rosetta-code-challenges/longest-common-subsequence"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}